metadata.editComments:
Wow! Now that's what you call a song!
The artists are actually Disclosure, Sam Smith, Nile Rodgers and Jimmy Napes. I've put only one of them not to make a mess in the database.
I feel like the first guitar chord is actually Dbmaj7/Bb.
Not sure about the melody in the 5th measure and the diminished G chord.
